  "description": "Remodels Flowers and other Plants into cute 3D models in the style of Allure!",
  "body": "<center>\n<h1><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/125e225c230845b5c04ce12b6a1efc9479dc2ceb.png\" alt=\"Allure micropacks\"></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-3d-plants/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8a2dd1324a19f7594a6e032659b78fb3e5e89a2d.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/allure-6439754/\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/48f3ed3f11e619ef7fea93c4344ae8f4ba233cb0.png\" alt=\"Planet Minecraft\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/p4ncake\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1fab8f2e1518ab9f6373586085d9aa785e0e3b9d.png\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-Fi\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f5a8b8552da877af71a331499e3fffcb57b513a.png\" alt=\"Join our Community on Discord!\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Allure 3D Plants</strong> is a part of a bigger project called <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\">Allure</a>. The pack contains 3D plants designed in the same style as Allure has and it develops alongside Allure. The pack aims to make plants look better without overdoing the modeling.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/VhLFOwiA/images/d0d575ebac018eb634d3ed6f7197e03d5bf5f9fd.jpeg\" alt=\"Flowers Screenshot\"><hr><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/VhLFOwiA/images/84e4d34a8a43be3998420a9516be70f5cce9f0c8.png\"></p>  \n<hr>\n<p><br>Please also check out <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack/\">Allure</a>, you might enjoy it! If you want to get notified for updates on the pack progress, give me suggestions or you wanna report any bugs, consider joining my Discord server <a href=\"https://discord.gg/C9Q6XFG8T8\">here</a>!</p>\n<br><br><hr>\n<h1>Other Projects!</h1>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure 3D Plants\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab67244910ef4ab4fca79d7e98f4f7afbe9a75ec.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-emoji-pack\"><img alt=\"Allure Emoji Pack\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/62de9de72ccd55e8a14fd4b637eb9c54dd0fb888.png\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-dark-theme-gui\"><img alt=\"Allure Dark Theme GUI\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f8deee765f891b6ca092c2ae5c120c8ea01c9007.webp\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/allure-fresh-animations-support\"><img alt=\"Allure Fresh Animations Support\" src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a4b12553ad59462994b06b9f7124fd36c9a81138.webp\"></a>\n</center>",
